{"tid":1423677,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如何反駁電筒武器論","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T08:02:57.000Z","uid":289857,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a3119c68b59d6c2491a57707a9bf2df3c1950c70","tid":1423677,"uid":289857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gbd527c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgbd527c.jpg&h=d85a164b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係咁，香港就無罪推論原則嘅<br />\n一日你無證據佢買依啲電筒 係想用黎射啲汪汪<br />\n你都唔可以禁止佢買依啲電筒<br />\n可能某啲人慣左&quot;陽光&quot;司法????<br />\n仲有，你班友知強光入眼係會有損健康嘅<br />\n班狗用閃光燈同強燈射記者同示威者你唔出聲?<br />\n好憎依啲 無腦言論 無原則扮有<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得仲有咩可以反駁?<br />\n雖然佢地都係選擇性失明失聰嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗定點勸啲淺藍長輩都好吖"},{"pid":"34d7d55a1aa74408eda46dd884cbdb02440a8578","tid":1423677,"uid":37537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"直接屈返佢手機閃光燈傷人囉"},{"pid":"9570af5a6ffeff592bb36f237e8c2aa7ba67a8a7","tid":1423677,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:37:34.000Z","msg":"點解要反駁<br />\n而家係唔係買嘢都要冇自由<br />\n一係你就出禁刀令"},{"pid":"e1d7f4b2d633c23726fb4ee11839576d1b01a319","tid":1423677,"uid":16041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"就黎有手有腳就拉"},{"pid":"a5cde0571d62336193ac7f1fc2d1453b7aa25717","tid":1423677,"uid":39182,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:41:12.000Z","msg":"無需要反駁，記者昨晚已經一路追住問，憑咩去假定會有攻擊行為? 同埋點樣合理懷疑?<br />\n<br />\n就算話有人用laser 射眼會傷害黑警，咁有無證據買 laser 既人係會做/已做出相關行為?<br />\n<br />\n無既話可以做文宣去街市同師奶講，買菜刀都犯法，實際例子有新疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01f04ff82bd19807cf88aef591557b9283d132","tid":1423677,"uid":194669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"1. 問鐳射電筒點解係攻擊性武器？ 如果答會射到眼盲。<br />\n<br />\n咁你問用咩攻擊眼會唔令到眼盲，手指插眼都可以令人盲，咁係唔係唔可以帶手指出街"},{"pid":"1c9fb1096931c66d03603a1984e3ebce2c7b7b9d","tid":1423677,"uid":258999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"無讀過大學既人，唔會明觀星筆係ocamp物資"},{"pid":"7bea1a0406c70d62cec15b40b047983e76545c1f","tid":1423677,"uid":170320,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"有人用鉛筆做功課，有人用鉛筆黎殺人。咁係咪唔再比人寫字呀<br />\n咁全部小朋友唔比佢地做功課，尤其係16歲以下既小朋友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLHCdvH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLHCdvH.png&h=0d55d6a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8a4a33afd32a8acc9c97ec29b3a3383389cd7f3","tid":1423677,"uid":11719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"好荒謬，懷疑就拉，完全唔需要證據，男人有碌鳩就合理懷疑企圖強姦？女人有西就合理懷疑賣淫？<br />\n<br />\n香港係幾時開始變到要揾證據證明自屘無犯法己"},{"pid":"0c08e3a7ac819999fe04914ae9aa1ce62f60f532","tid":1423677,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:57:24.000Z","msg":"四個碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4997bdaad92aa61293a5ce5a62f2e637f707abb","tid":1423677,"uid":117265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"其實暴簡單用番721果單野就證明到警方係選擇性執法"},{"pid":"f93ab77de480f2a1ca62473927ac43cd7a5d52b5","tid":1423677,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"有恐怖分子亂用槍械傷人，所以揸槍既都係恐怖分子，啲黑警係恐怖分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cdc4df85f28346f637ea196cd0881f0cc0532a","tid":1423677,"uid":29942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗駁<br />\n呢啲人一開始已經先入為主，唔會接受人講解"},{"pid":"87edb086000f6106990ab1a430ae355bba97b80c","tid":1423677,"uid":130797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"傻西黎<br />\n法例無禁止就即係合法<br />\n你吹得過我係做收藏用途呀<br />\n<br />\n而家大埔有人車d屎過去警犬度呀<br />\n咁去捉哂爆石既人丫笨柒<br />\n<br />\n尋晚嬲撚到而家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ab6361bd935909954eba51d36f9f31b184cf49","tid":1423677,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:23:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推</strong></span>"},{"pid":"259b2446acba621a4e8052ab7d9aa866eafb4bef","tid":1423677,"uid":50608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"買100枝都得 派學校一齊觀星"},{"pid":"b5cdaa61e157ff7cf12c07b6ac75edf4d4af8a81","tid":1423677,"uid":190604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:35:57.000Z","msg":"佢要用雷射筆攻擊人<br />\n個電筒先叫武器<br />\n如果你話平時有人用雷射筆攻擊警察<br />\n而見到呢個人買雷射筆就話佢係管有武器<br />\n係邏輯謬誤<br />\n<br />\n正如佢地警察宿舍有中年人掉玻璃樽空襲示威者<br />\n係咪可以拉晒所有持有玻璃樽嘅中年人？<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係先入為主，係邏輯謬誤<br />\n講唔通<br />\n因為佢真係無攻擊呢個行為"},{"pid":"a5a4da7bb1bb7596fa5cef1c2cbe8f4cd23767a6","tid":1423677,"uid":285864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"而家係咪未犯事先拉人？<br />\n講係定唔係就得。<br />\n買十幾枝鐳射筆有冇犯法？<br />\n如果冇，佢當時有冇用鐳射筆攻擊任何人？<br />\n如果冇，你拉乜野？"},{"pid":"87c7c8b0a1b374e84f6a55d40523579d592bc676","tid":1423677,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"記者必須向警方查詢浸大學生會會長購買嘅觀星筆嘅功率。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426745\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}